Aim:- WRITE A PROGRAM TO DEMONSTRATE DATAFRAME CREATION AND VISUALIZATION USING PANDAS AND MATPLOTLIB

ALGORITHM:-

STEP 1: start the program
STEP 2: import required libraries (pandas, numpy, matplotlib)
STEP 3: create data using numpy array
STEP 4: create dataframe using pandas
STEP 5: convert runs column into integer type
STEP 6: display the dataframe
STEP 7: create bar chart using matplotlib
STEP 8: label x-axis, y-axis and title
STEP 9: display the graph
STEP 10: stop the program

#CODE
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

data = np.array([["CSK", 195], ["MI", 150], ["RCB", 200], ["KKR", 170]])
df = pd.DataFrame(data, columns=["Team", "Runs"])
df["Runs"] = df["Runs"].astype(int)

print(df)

plt.bar(df["Team"], df["Runs"])
plt.xlabel("Team")
plt.ylabel("Run")
plt.title("IPL Team Runs")
plt.show()


